| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6361 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 63e9b6a8-a36a-5445-b245-e82795e09ee5"
